          <title>Gerrit Cole will miss 2025 MLB season as Yankees announce ace will undergo Tommy John surgery</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The New York Yankees&apos; worst fears came true, as they announced Gerrit Cole will undergo Tommy John surgery on Tuesday to repair a torn UCL, rendering him out for the entire 2025 season.]]></description>
