          <title>QB Sam Darnold agrees on a 3-year, $100.5 million deal with Seahawks, AP source says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Seattle Seahawks have found the replacement for Geno Smith, agreeing to a three-year, $100.5 million contract with Sam Darnold, a person with knowledge of the deal told The Associated Press on Monday.]]></description>
